title: YEHANTI Personalised Pet ID Tags - Engraved Dog & Cat Name Tags, Silent Slide, 4 Lines Text - No Jingling (Black-Black, L)
features: No Jingling Pet Tag: Our Cute Silent Pet ID Tags are not only fashionable but also silent, with a no-jingling silicone band. Keep your home quieter with this indoor dog tag that's perfect for reducing pet noise when your pet moves around.

Dog Tag Size Guide: Available in 3 sizes for small and large pets, these customise ID tags fit a variety of collar and harnesses widths. Small: fits 5/8 inch wide collars. Medium: fits 3/4 inch wide collars. Large: fits 1 inch wide collars.

Dog Tags Material Info: The metal part of the dog id tag is made of black/silver plated matte finish stainless steel which is better quality than brass, aluminum or alloy materials. The premium, soft and stretchable silicone band keep the tag safe and quiet to your pet. No fade, no tarnish, no allergies.

Laser Engraved Dog Tags: Unleash your furry friend's style with our engraved dog name tags! You can write your pet's name, your phone number, address, microchipped and some information to ask for help. Give your pet the ultimate accessory with our custom engraved dog tags today!

Ideal Present for Pet Enthusiasts: This personalised dog tags and cat tags makes a thoughtful and cherished gift for pet parents, family members, and close friends. Its unique customization makes it a perfect present for various occasions such as birthdays, pet adoption anniversaries, or as a token of appreciation for fellow animal lovers.
